					</a>
	</h3>
    	    <div class="summary">
		   <p><p>Dear Authors, Reviewers, and Readers,</p>
<p>We are pleased to inform you that <em>KONSELOR</em> Journal is currently undergoing the <strong>Re-Accreditation</strong> process with the Ministry of Education and Culture of the Republic of Indonesia to maintain our <strong>SINTA 2</strong> status. This process has been ongoing since our submission in June 2024, reflecting our commitment to upholding academic excellence and quality standards.</p>
<p>We deeply appreciate your continued trust and support, which play a vital role in this journey. We will keep you updated on the progress and remain grateful for your contributions to the journal's success.</p>
<p>Warm regards,<br /><em>KONSELOR Editorial Team</em></p></p>
	    </div>
    	
